    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so pointless lately. like, i was reading about entropy and heat death again, and it just hit me how much of a joke everything is. we struggle, we hurt, we try to build things, but in the end the universe is just going to be cold and dead and none of it will have mattered. why even bother waking up tomorrow if the outcome is already decided?",
